Discover AudioMirror peers on the local network via mDNS.

Example: audiomirror-cli discover --duration-secs 5

Usage: audiomirror-cli discover [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --duration-secs <DURATION_SECS>
          [default: 5]

      --signaling-port <SIGNALING_PORT>
          [default: 7000]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
